verbs.description: [V: shsu] resubmits med school accreditation application sam houston state university has resubmitted its initial application for the accreditation of its proposed medical school after the first was kicked back for falling short of newly implemented standards the commission on osteopathic college accreditation turned down sam houston state submission for new medical school candidacy status at its august meeting the association confirmed this week such candidacy status is the first of two coca houston university of houston university of new england college of osteopathic medicine dr charles henley texas higher education coordinating board huntsville university proposed school university of north texas health science center conroe coheed and cambria sam houston johnson development corp developer school grand central park university of accreditation sam houston state university huntsville universitys proposed school liaison committee for medical education coca college of osteopathic medicine san antonio texas
